quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,10,"Yye yooyo abatonnyeseza enkuba okuva waggulu, ku nkuba eyo kwe munywa, era ku nkuba eyo emiti kwe gimerera nga ku gyo kwe muliisa ensolo za mmwe"
  16,11,"Abamereza nayo ebirimwa ne Zaituni n'emitende ne nzabibu nabuli bibala byonna, mazima mu ekyo mulimu akabonero (akalaga obuyinza) bwa Katonda eri abantu abafumiitiriza"
  16,12,Era yabagondeza ekiro n'emisana era enjuba n'omwezi n'emmunyeenye byonna byagonzebwa (bitambulira) ku kiragiro kye. Mazima mu ebyo byonna mulimu obubonero eri abantu abategeera
  16,13,"N’ebyo bye yabateera mu nsi nga amabala g'abyo tegafaanagana, mazima mu ekyo mulimu akabonero eri abantu abejjukanya"
  16,14,"Era yye, yooyo eyagonza enyanja mube nga mulya muyo ennyama (ebyenyanja) ebibisi era muggye mu yo eby'okwewunda bye mwambala. Ogenda noolaba amaato nga gakola ekkubo muyo, olwo nno musobole okugenda okunoonya ebigabwabye (Katonda), era kibasobozese okwebaza"
  16,15,"Era yassa mu nsi enkondo (ensozi) ereme kubayuuza, era nassaamu emigga, n'amakubo musobole okulungama"
  16,16,"Era naateeka (mu nsi) obubonero, okwo nno bwogattako emmunyeenye basobole okumanya gye balaga"
  16,17,Abange oyo atonda ayinza okuba nga atatonda! abaffe temujjukira
  16,18,"Ne bwe mubala ebyengera bya Katonda temusobola kubikomekkereza, mazima Katonda musonyiyi nnyo musaasizi"
  16,19,Era Katonda amanyi bye mukola mu kyama ne bye mukola mu lwatu
  16,20,Era abo bebasaba nebaleka Katonda tebatonda kintu kyonna ate nga bo batondebwa butondebwa
  16,21,(Bebasaba) bafu ssi balamu era tebamanyi ddi lwe balizuukizibwa